summary:
Adds a Dwemerish player home West from Windhelm.
Now equipped with maid twins.
descriptionHtml:
========================================Description=========================================
The Skywatch Manor is a hidden building which belonged to your mysterious \'Friend\'. 
It has all that an adventurous Dovahkiin needs, including twins! =3

Located west from Windhelm near Dwemer ruins. Has two vendors who sell smithing and alchemy suplies as well as sweep the floors. On the bed you can find traveling clothes that work well in snowstorms. 
============================================================================================

This is my second mod made for Skyrim.
I have tested it several times, but some bugs might appear. 
If you encounter any bugs or other issues comments would be appreciated.


Thank you in advance for downloading. Please enjoy.
============================================================================================
